/-- The algebra isomorphism `adjoin ‚Ñ§ {Œ∂} ‚âÉ‚Çê[‚Ñ§] (ùìû K)`, where `Œ∂` is a primitive `p ^ k`-th root of
unity and `K` is a `p ^ k`-th cyclotomic extension of `‚Ñö`. -/
@[simps]
