#align is_primitive_root.adjoin_equiv_ring_of_integers IsPrimitiveRoot.adjoinEquivRingOfIntegers

/-- The ring of integers of a `p ^ k`-th cyclotomic extension of `‚Ñö` is a cyclotomic extension. -/
